State of Connecticut v. Gilberto Rodriguez, Jr. (7906)

Borden, Norcott and Foti, Js.

Argued October 11 decision released October 18, 1989 David M. Abbamonte, for the appellant (defendant). RitaM. Shair, deputy assistant state’s attorney, with whom, on the brief, were Donald A. Browne, state’s attorney, and Richard Palombo, assistant state’s attorney, for the appellee (state). Per Curiam.

There is no error.
